06:37.280 --> 06:40.840
to mobile Linux OSes lacking what we would consider

06:40.840 --> 06:44.200
really kind of table stakes standard security features

06:44.200 --> 06:45.880
in Android or iOS.

06:45.880 --> 06:47.960
