08:36.780 --> 08:38.220
which means I still haven't shifted

08:38.220 --> 08:41.300
a majority of my workflows off the desktop, you know?

08:41.300 --> 08:42.700
And so there is kind of that balance.

08:42.700 --> 08:43.940
Like I want security,

08:43.940 --> 08:46.020
but I want it in the way that I can opt into it

08:46.020 --> 08:47.220
and I'm aware of it.

08:47.220 --> 08:48.900
